dct_description_sm: Property map of Loch Arbour in Ocean Township NJ. At the time, this tract was owned by Samuel Johnson. The land was first surveyed by Herman Lehlbach in 1883. Lehlbach Brothers did a revised survey at the time of the map's 1898 creation.
